yne\", \"from\": 229, \"to\": 234}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The image of Owens-8 feet high and 15 feet wide-is the first thing people see when entering the headquarters of the architectural glass manufacturer.\", \"from\": 249, \"to\": 398, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The image\", \"from\": 249, \"to\": 258}, {\"ngram\": \"Owens-8 feet\", \"from\": 262, \"to\": 274}, {\"ngram\": \"the first thing\", \"from\": 300, \"to\": 315}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 316, \"to\": 322}, {\"ngram\": \"the headquarters\", \"from\": 341, \"to\": 357}, {\"ngram\": \"the architectural glass manufacturer\", \"from\": 361, \"to\": 397}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The wall includes four panels of digitally printed glass that combine to create the overall image.\", \"from\": 399, \"to\": 497, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The wall\", \"from\": 399, \"to\": 407}, {\"ngram\": \"four panels\", \"from\": 417, \"to\": 428}, {\"ngram\": \"digitally printed glass\", \"from\": 432, \"to\": 455}, {\"ngram\": \"the overall image\", \"from\": 479, \"to\": 496}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The glass is installed with Bendheim's TurnKey Fusion Light Wall system, which uses petite clips to capture the glass, eliminating the need for adhesives or expensive glass drilling.\", \"from\": 498, \"to\": 680, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 545, \"end\": 551, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fusion_power\", \"score\": 0.7884949942249037, \"rank\": 0.135377375718081, \"text\": \"Fusion\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fusion_power\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fusion_power\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The glass\", \"from\": 498, \"to\": 507}, {\"ngram\": \"petite clips\", \"from\": 582, \"to\": 594}, {\"ngram\": \"the glass\", \"from\": 606, \"to\": 615}, {\"ngram\": \"the need\", \"from\": 629, \"to\": 637}, {\"ngram\": \"adhesives\", \"from\": 642, \"to\": 651}, {\"ngram\": \"expensive glass drilling\", \"from\": 655, \"to\": 679}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The project captures Owens as he competes en route to four gold medals at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 682, \"to\": 769, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The project\", \"from\": 682, \"to\": 693}, {\"ngram\": \"Owens\", \"from\": 703, \"to\": 708}, {\"ngram\": \"route\", \"from\": 727, \"to\": 732}, {\"ngram\": \"four gold medals\", \"from\": 736, \"to\": 752}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 756, \"to\": 768}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He won individual gold medals in the 100 and 200 meters and long jump.\", \"from\": 770, \"to\": 840, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"individual gold medals\", \"from\": 777, \"to\": 799}, {\"ngram\": \"the 100 and 200 meters\", \"from\": 803, \"to\": 825}, {\"ngram\": \"long jump\", \"from\": 830, \"to\": 839}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He also ran on the victorious 4 x 100-meter relay.\", \"from\": 841, \"to\": 891, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the victorious 4 x 100-meter relay\", \"from\": 856, \"to\": 890}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Berlin Games were held amid a politically charged atmosphere, coming just three years after Adolf Hitler was appointed chancellor of Germany.\", \"from\": 892, \"to\": 1037, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 988, \"end\": 1000, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adolf_Hitler\", \"score\": 0.9999999999552074, \"rank\": 4.43361696635104e-11, \"text\": \"Adolf Hitler\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adolf_Hitler\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adolf_Hitler\"}, {\"begin\": 1029, \"end\": 1036, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nazi_Germany\", \"score\": 0.9422196509049783, \"rank\": 0.06128428279634872, \"text\": \"Germany\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nazi_Germany\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nazi_Germany\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Berlin Games\", \"from\": 892, \"t